        <warning-info>
            <text type="warning_title">Road Weather Alert for Adelaide</text>
            <text type="warning_advice">
                <p>The SA Police advises that people should:</p>
                <p>Slow down and take extra care.</p>
                <p>Maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle in front.</p>
                <p>Turn on your headlights.</p>
            </text>
            <text type="warning_advice_contact">For information on any road closures, please contact your local council or the Police.</text>
            <text type="warning_next_issue">The next alert will be issued by 5:00 pm CST Saturday.</text>
        </warning-info>
